&gt;Emily vanishes into the nearest wall.  After a short delay, she sticks her head back out, blushing bright blue.
&gt;&quot;N-now, this was a gift.  Please do not think less of me for how revealing it is.&quot;
&gt;&quot;I&#039;m sure it&#039;s fine.&quot;
