&gt;&quot;Splendid!  Could you elaborate a little?&quot;
&gt;She gestures as if to speak, but immediately covers her mouth again.

&gt;&quot;Take your time, miss.  We&#039;re not in a hurry, sorry if we&#039;re rushing you.&quot;
